Value.value: Greetings, traveler! Take a drink, rest your legs, have a smoke!
Pick whatever is on the slab and stay out of my way!
I am sooo bored with this drab little hamlet. Bring me flowers and you'll get a kiss!
Flowers?! *gives you a kiss* How nice! If you buy me a red dress I will take you to the ball in Nes'ek...
O, doesn't it look lovely on me? Now, if I only had some matching red dancing shoes!
The shoes... you are a hero! *gives you a kiss* I don't dare to ask for earrings now... *flutters her eyelashes*
What a beautiful earrings. O... *hits forehead* ... the ball was YESTERDAY! Umm.. thanks for the presents, I really appreciate it!
